[No. 6,449. Department One.] JAMES LANE v. PAUL PFERDNER State Lands. Appeal from a judgment for the plaintiff, and an order denying a new trial, in the First District Court, County of San Luis Obispo. Fawcett, J.

Charles E. Wilson, and McD. R. Venable, for Appellant.

W. J. & William Graves, for Respondent.

The Court:

Upon the authority of Lane v. Pferdner, 56 Cal. 122; judgment and order affirmed.
